<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <style>
        @page {
            size: A4;
            margin: 20mm 15mm;
        }
        body {
            font-family: 'Inter', Arial, 'Latha', sans-serif;
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #1e293b;
            line-height: 1.6;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }
        .header {
            text-align: center;
            border-bottom: 2px solid #254aa0;
            padding-bottom: 10px;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }
        .bank-name {
            font-size: 18px;
            font-weight: 800;
            color: #254aa0;
            margin: 0;
            text-transform: uppercase;
        }
        .office-name {
            font-size: 14px;
            font-weight: 700;
            margin: 5px 0;
        }
        .reference-section {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            font-weight: 700;
        }
        .letter-content {
            margin-bottom: 40px;
        }
        .recipient {
            margin-bottom: 25px;
        }
        .subject {
            text-align: center;
            font-weight: 800;
            text-decoration: underline;
            margin-bottom: 25px;
            padding: 0 40px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
        }
        .salutation {
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }
        .body-text {
            text-align: justify;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        .observations-box {
            background-color: #f8fafc;
            border: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .observation-title {
            font-weight: 800;
            color: #254aa0;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            text-decoration: underline;
        }
        .signature-section {
            margin-top: 50px;
            text-align: right;
        }
        .sig-block {
            display: inline-block;
            text-align: center;
            min-width: 200px;
        }
        .sig-line {
            border-top: 1px solid #000;
            margin-top: 50px;
            margin-bottom: 5px;
        }
        .trilingual-header {
            font-size: 10px;
            color: #64748b;
            margin-bottom: 2px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="header">
        <div class="trilingual-header">
            {{organization.bankNameTa}} | {{organization.bankNameHi}}
        </div>
        <p class="bank-name">{{organization.bankNameEn}}</p>
        <p class="office-name">{{organization.officeNameEn}}</p>
        <div class="trilingual-header" style="margin-top: 5px;">
            {{organization.officeNameTa}} | {{organization.officeNameHi}}
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="reference-section">
        <div>Ref: RO/VISIT/OBS/{{refNo}}</div>
        <div>Date: {{currentDate}}</div>
    </div>

    <div class="recipient">
        <p>The Branch Manager,</p>
        <p><strong>{{branchName}} ({{branchCode}})</strong></p>
    </div>

    <div class="subject">
        Subject: Observations made during Management Visit on {{visitDate}} - Reg.
    </div>

    <div class="letter-content">
        <p class="salutation">Sir / Madam,</p>

        <p class="body-text">
            During the management visit undertaken at your branch on <strong>{{visitDate}}</strong> by <strong>{{visitorName}}</strong> ({{visitorRole}}), the following key observations/non-compliances were noted. You are advised to take immediate corrective action and submit your point-wise reply/compliance status to this office for our records.
        </p>

        <div class="observations-box">
            <div class="observation-title">KEY OBSERVATIONS / POINTS FOR RECTIFICATION</div>
            <div style="white-space: pre-wrap; min-height: 100px;">{{observations}}</div>
        </div>

        <p class="body-text">
            Kindly ensure that all the above-mentioned points are addressed within <strong>7 working days</strong> from the date of this letter. Any persistent non-compliance will be viewed seriously by the Regional Management.
        </p>
    </div>

    <p>Yours faithfully,</p>

    <div class="signature-section">
        <div class="sig-block">
            <div class="sig-line"></div>
            <p><strong>{{visitorName}}</strong></p>
            <p>{{visitorDesignation}}</p>
            <p>{{organization.officeNameEn}}</p>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div style="margin-top: 30px; font-size: 10px; color: #94a3b8; border-top: 1px dashed #e2e8f0; padding-top: 10px;">
        This is an electronically generated letter from the Regional Performance Portal and does not require a physical signature.
    </div>

</body>
</html>
